\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I should say we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me something about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - regularly you - o
ne was - one had to do one job and one another, I mean - the weekly ritual of cleaning knives and forks. Scrubbing - all sorts of things really. Helping with the washing and - running errands, all sorts of thing we had to do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have your own particular jobs to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Each child had its own particular thing did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did the se jobs change as children got older, did they sort of inherit a new job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, as they got older - boys being the first, they went to work and it - sort of passed down really to us, younger ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What sort of work did the boys do at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well they had to do - scrubbing the same as the girls. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you remember any distinction your mother made between what boys should do and what girls should do in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 There were certain things were men's work and women's work, but for children it was all the same was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Boys washed up too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you get any money for doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It wasn't like earning your pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no. There was no pocket money those - excuse me - about - a penny a week, ha'penny a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And it wasn't in any way connected with the jobs you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You talked about the weekly ritual of cleaning, was this done on a Friday or Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Fridays or Saturdays mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 The house was done out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But - the ordinary washing up and that was - every day. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I have heard of a system of giving the house a good clean out before the weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
No, it was done through the week, it was just - such jobs as - as I say, cleaning the cutlery or - doing the brass-work and all sorts of things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 After you left school and started work did you continue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Continue it? Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You were quite near the top of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Fourth down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember doing things to help the little ones in the family when they were babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Always had to take them out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was there a pram?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Anything else you did for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well I had to do - some of the washing, part of the washing and - all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever sort of put them to bed and bath them or wash them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, wash them and bath them but I can't remember about putting them to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was there any one particular sort of younger child that you did more than the others that you remember or were closer to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. I don't think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It was all just what came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember when you were little any of the older ones doing things for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember any of the little ones doing things for you, running errands for you or looking after anything for you,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No. I had to - run errands for me older brother as he got older but I can't remember - them doing anything -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you enjoy doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, it's a matter of duty, you just - just adjusted and - didn't notice it, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you remember anything about bedtime, and what sort of time for example you were supposed to be in bed or was that not particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh we were all put to bed reasonably early, that's - as far as I can remember but - the time I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you know if it varied in summer and winter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Think the - the older ones I think - you stayed later as you got older, stayed up later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't remember at what age you saw yourself off to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you share the bedroom or bed with anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Three in a bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that girls or boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you describe how the three bedrooms were used when you were all at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well parents in one naturally. And - the boys in another and girls shared the other one between them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your parents ever have a little one in with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh - yes, a baby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You mentioned earlier on that there was no bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me how the family managed about baths?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, they used to put the bath - in - in front of the fire like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 In what you called then the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that done at regular intervals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, regular - intervals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was there a particular night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mostly Friday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have hot water out of a tap or did it have to be heated up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no. Had to be heated.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did all of you bath on the same night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well, no I don't think so, only the younger ones but of course you see - the elder ones grew up and went out to work and - they wouldn't be there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But the younger children would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Did your mother have a sort of routine of when she gave clean clothes, when you had clean clothes when you were little, clean underclothes and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, I suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember that, if it was after the bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh would be, yes. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You ate in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever eat in any other room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, in the sitting room if - at times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What sort of occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well it would be - perhaps Sundays or - any parties or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was the sitting room kept as a rather special room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. What they called the parlour in those days. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't often hear that word now do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it a room where you couldn't go sort of and play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, you wasn't allowed in there to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 On Sundays did you usually sit in there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Young children as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your parents sit in there in the evenings ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, only weekends it was used, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me what sort of cooking equipment your mother had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Ordinary gas stove and a - a kitchen range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did she cook on both at the same time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me something about the meals, for example, when was breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh round about I suppose - eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Who was present for that meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well all of us - really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Father too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Had he gone to work earlier and come back,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. It would be before he went to work. As far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Then you went off to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you take anything for dinner or did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, regular home to dinner and regular at twelve o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that a cooked meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What did you normally have for breakfast during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Porridge or - toast, things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Any tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 On Sundays was there anything different for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, yes, as far as I can remember we always had - a
 cooked breakfast and - we had a luxury of tea and cakes in bed Sunday mornings. Yes. All - fancy biscuits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that brought up to you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 By your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What age did you have to be before you qualified for that, quite young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, as far as I can remember always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That wasn't instead of breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, that was - yes, that wasn't instead of breakfast. Mostly eggs we had I think for breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And at midday dinner can you tell me the sort of food your mother would give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Yes, we had good meals and a sweet, we'd have - stews and - meat puddings, meat pies, all that sort of thing. A real good - meal, you know, and always a sweet - like bread and butter pudding, rice puddings, all that type of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you usually have a vegetable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Two vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 On Sunday was there anything different at dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh well it was always the - the big roast dinner Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Anything different for Sunday sweet at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well all 
much the same really, I mean - we'd have - hot or cold plum duff, which would be - nowadays would be - currant pudding or - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You then went back to school and came home after school, what sort of food was there for the remainder of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh - only bread and - margarine really, teatime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Nothing else after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So the main meal was the midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your father have anything extra in the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, he always had something with his tea you know like - fish or eggs or something like that, he always had a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 A bit extra?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would your mother have some of that too with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, not very often, mostly him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did he have tea with you in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well I suppose round about - five-ish, half past five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 His day was over by then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm. Well, I say yes, sometimes he used to go back - after tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Then on Sundays was tea also bread and marg or was there anything extra?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh there might have been jam, oh no, jam and cake and that - Sundays, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And ordinary midday dinner, was your father there too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Sunday, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And on weekdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So father was always at all meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your mother or your father ever bake any bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Any jam made?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It wasn't really economical in towns I believe to buy the stuff and make it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Bottled fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Pickles? Do you ever remember any brewing of beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Or home made wines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your mother ever make any medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you ever dosed with anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Used to have regular doses of liquorice powder.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But that was bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did the call it Spanish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I think it's a different sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well liquorice powder was a - brownish yellowish powder they used to make up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Tastes like liquorice does it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Yes. Not very pleasant, or - senna - tea, otherwise. But they made that a ritual once a week, you had to have medicine, why I do not know but -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you know if that's still done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You think it's gone out now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It was very widespread I believe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, I don't know why they made such a ritual of that, everybody. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was anything grown in the way of vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember eating any tinned vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Dried fruit of course would be in puddings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Any dried vegetables do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. I don't think there was such things in those days, there used to be - packets of - peas, what they called
 marrowfat peas and they used to be soaked - with a little - square I think carbonate. Yes, and - mother used to buy 'em in packets. Marrowfat peas. But apart from those peas, or - we used to eat - eat a lot of - butter beans and haricot beans. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about livestock, no pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, chickens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You had some chickens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, that's where we used to get our eggs from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it enough for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your mother didn't need to buy eggs?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh she may have done, I don't suppose all the year round thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever eat those fowls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Who looked after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 How many times a week do you think you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Every day practically.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Even on Friday and every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Don't think there was such a thing. Tinned meat. Corned beef you bought loose and - it wasn't such, you know, you didn't buy it in tins in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever have it loose in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever get some extra meat such as rabbit from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh - what - in town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember ever seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 She stinted herself did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm. Very often went without for the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember whether she tried to conceal the fact?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your father had a bit extra at tea time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did he have more generally, bigger helpings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Well the whole - household centred round the fathers in those days. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well no, they were very strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What sort of conversation was allowed, were any words allowed to be spoken?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well - regards children, we - nothing much was said was there, it was - children should be seen and not heard. That was the slogan in those days. Same as our tea, we - we couldn't have a cup of tea - with our meal, 
we had to wait - 'til the grown ups had had theirs and then ours had to be watered. And you mustn't answer back in those days either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you ever remember doing so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - well if you did it was very - you was reprimanded - very severely too. That wasn't allowed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did they tend to explain things to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 If you asked the reason why you had to do something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You were just given your orders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You said no speaking at meals, you could ask for things though could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did they tend to talk to each other meals or did everybody sit pretty quietly?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - as far as I remember it was - just a quiet meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Oh no. No, you had to have what you was given. The same as you always had to say grace, before and after. You wasn't allowed - to get from the table until you did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did each child say grace individually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not all together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was there a particular order in which this was said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well I suppose - we - we all said it together as far as I can remember. Mm. Like - each one, of the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it the same form of words before and after the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't remember what it was do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 For what we are about to receive, the Lord must make us truly thankful. And - for what we have received at the end you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your parents say it too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So there was no picking and choosing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You weren't asked if you'd like a bit of this or that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, because if we didn't - didn't like it we didn't have it, naturally. But we - you had to go without then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They didn't really mind if you refused food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, but - you couldn't have anything in preference.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I think that's a sensible rule in some ways.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well it is really, I mean the meal was cooked and that was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember ever leaving food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, because - stew particularly I didn't like stew and I could never eat it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What was your parents reaction to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well I had to go without 'til the next meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They didn't actually punish you for leaving food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, no, you just - went without.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you ask for things to be passed to you that were on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You didn't have to wait until they asked you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you ask for more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you expected to sit in a particular way at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, sit 'til everybody else was finished, naturally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about how you sat, did they mind if you had your elbows on the table and sat forward or leant back, that type of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, as far as I remember they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They liked you to sit up straight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about your knife and fork and spoon and that sort of thing, were they fussy about the way you ate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No. Just ordinary.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you ever bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Could you leave the table when you'd finished or when everybody else had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When everybody had finished. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did everybody sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you always have the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me how the meal was served? Was it from the pots onto your plates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 In the scullery would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Then brought in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it given to you in any particular order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Not that I can remember.
