No, my mother was a bit on the - more on the religious side, she - you know, we didn't hear a lot of swearing, no, lose their temper at times you know with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about generally round about you, did you hear much swearing at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I can't remember a lot of swearing can you Fred? Around about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Such a thing wasn't discussed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They didn't discuss it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What do you think in the way they brought you up they sort of felt were the important things in life?
