\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So as far as their ideas about the sort of children they were trying to bring up you don't know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, it was - I don't think it was ever discussed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't remember them talking about things like honesty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. And we weren't - you know, I man - if you told a lie that was dreadful, you was brought up, you k
now, not to tell lies and all that sort of thing. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They did make rather a point of that did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, yes, definitely. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What other things were bad, or good, do you remember about general conduct?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - don't really know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was religion mentioned at all ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, 'cs - as I say we had - we had to go to school - to Sunday school regularly and - all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When you had a birthday would it be different form any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, you alwa
ys got - a present, or probably it wasn't much but it was to you and - a few copper - well - if you were given tuppence that was - a fortune really, to spend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have anything special to eat at tea on a birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I can't remember that but w
e always had - always had Christmas parties, you now, a Christmas tree and - party like, that sort of thing Christmas time but - about birthdays - I can't remember. May have done on the Sunday. No, I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So as far as you remember there wasn't a birthday party?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But there was at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, we always had a - well a - mostly a Christmas tree - just after Christmas you know-for children to come and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would that be sort of neighbours children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And relatives, did they come then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No. More children, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 At Christmas did you go visiting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You stayed home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Stayed home and - had a - well - was always plenty of - fruit and - all extras you k
now Quite a ritual Christmas time 'cos it'd take you nearly a week getting the Christmas pudding mixtures ready. I mean there was nothing - prepared like to - these days, I mean even you - had to sit one evening stoning raisins, another evening - you now,
 
chopping this up and chopping that up. See, things weren't - bought those days like they are now, there was nothing ready. Only - peel was bought - was bought in - like big pieces and that all had to be chopped and done. And sit and making paper chains fo
r about a - fortnight or three weeks beforehand. Which, to us children, was an adventure really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you all sort of take part in this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - yes, the elder ones. And - wouldn't think of buying - home made mince - shop mince meat. It all had to be home made.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about a cake, did you have that too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was there sort of stockings hung up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Not a lot in them but - still they was always hung up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Anything else you remember about Christmas Day that was different? Your father was at home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, and - mostly some relatives and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 From both sides of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, more from - mother's side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would they come for tea or dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Well they'd come and stay for the holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They came over and slept there did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Where could they sleep then, did they sleep in the parlour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, anywhere really you know for - just for the eve - evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Just for one evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was the tree in the parlour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you make all your own decorations for that?
