\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Novels mainly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did they have Marie Carelli or Annie Swann?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Not that I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you get Sunday school prizes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They were books weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Mostly - well you used to get prayer book or a Bible you know, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your mother and father ever read aloud to any of you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Any newspapers in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, always the Sunday newspaper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not a daily?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And any magazines or other kinds of periodicals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Just the Sunday newspaper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you remember which one it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, News of the World.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you allowed to read it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Good gracious no. Terrible if you picked that up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it sort of carefully kept then, suppose they finished
 with it and left it lying about, or didn't they, was it used for the fire or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well I suppose it was used for the fire eventually but - used to list - my father nearly all the week didn't it. He read a bit every night. No, but you - we weren't allowed to read 'til we got ever so old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was it much like it is now? A lot of scandal and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, similar sort of thing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember a funeral in the family before the end of 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, several.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you attend?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Before 1918? No, I can't remember - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You didn't attend any funerals up 'til then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did children not normally attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you wear any mourning clothes, black clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, you had to go in mourn
ing - well I don't know about when we were children, I can't - remember - as I say, I can't remember that but - in those days they went in mourning for twelve months didn't they. And then they'd go in half mourning for six months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your mother do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did people do that for children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, for everybody and you weren't allowed - to go to the pictures were you during the mourning period and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And your family observed that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm. I think they all did mostly those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember whether the blinds were drawn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And did the neighbours draw theirs as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Tha's a custom that has gone out now hasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, they don't - don't bother do they now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Is there anything else you can remember about the procedure of funerals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well - they always sent out black bordered envelopes - with a black bordered card. And you always got a black - you always got so many - memorial cards from the undertaker which
 you don't get now. You know, with the - number of the grave and all that sort of thing on.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were those given to relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, well they were - yes, they were given to - well the one that buried them you see like. Oh yes, and - yes, and then t
hey were given to relatives, I - in fact I've got some upstairs somewhere in a drawer. And always they had a black bordered handkerchief didn't they. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And after the funeral did they come back to the house for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You mentioned at Christmas relatives of your mother's would come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you ever taken out visiting relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, not as children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 At what sort of age would you go and visit relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh in our teens, you know, when we could go ourse
lves. But we were always taken - father always got - once a year - what they called a - well you wouldn't know, a wagonette.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I have seen them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Have you? Oh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I think there were different sized ones weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, there were. No, t
his - this - this would be a large one and once a year he used to hire it and take us - all out for a day. During the summer. Sometimes they had breaks wouldn't they for outings. What they called brakes, that was like a - bigger affair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That would be you and your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, all of us, that was a - the usual annual ritual you know, during the summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Where would you go then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, Hainault Forest or - Epping Forest or somewhere like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 A distance of about ten miles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, I suppose it would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would other relatives go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, just the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But the custom of sort of taking children to visit their relations, you didn't go for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, well for one thing was too many children wasn't there those days to take about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What were the relations that lived in London which you were in touch with in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well it would be my mother's sisters. Or brother-in-laws.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That was how many sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, she had three that I can remember but we - mostly only one came Christmas time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did they live in your part of London?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, the other side of London really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about your father, did he have family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 He had brothers but we never saw them 'til late - well very late in life, like - after the first world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They were also in London were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I suppose so, I don't really know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But they weren't part of your childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They weren't, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But your aunts were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 My mother's side.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about any grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I can only vaguely remember - one grandfather and then he died when I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 q}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 uite young. Otherwise I had no grandparents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you ever remember being taken out on shopping expeditions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Yes, for clothes you had to - be taken out for - buying clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Otherwise how was the shipping done for food and that kind of thing, did you do it when you got older, or did your mother do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well we all had to do it, I used to have to go and get - get the shopping before I went to school of a morning, go and get the - dinner.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It was done sort of daily was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. That had to be done before I went to school of a morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were the shops quite near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, there was - what - quarter of an hour's walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So it was quite a chore to do in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Yes, and then back again, then off to school which was about - twenty minutes walk I suppose. But there was no - nothing else to do, it was always walking, there was - no such things as - g
oing on buses or trams or anything in those days, not to school or anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And it was always bought sort of every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, and then you'd have to go in the afternoon - for something for father for tea. Perhaps another quarter of an hour to tw
enty minutes walk. Yes, special shops you had to go to didn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did they write it down in a book and you paid at the end of the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, no, paid for it as you bought it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have shops in your area where they mainly gave credit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, yes I suppose they did but I can - we never had that. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you shop at the Co-op at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Don't ever remember a Co-op in our day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It was mainly in the north they had them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Probably yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You were saying you used to go out with your father, did that happen quite often that he'd take you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh that would be - in me teenage - not as a child. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever go out on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Well, I say no, we used to go sometime - out - by o
urselves didn't we, as children, but not with parents. We used to go to Victoria Park and play sliding didn't we - as children. Well I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever go sort of out of London anywhere with perhaps when you were a teenager or a bit older on Bank Hol
iday excursions to the seaside or anything of that kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever go to the seaside as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, the first time I went - I can remember was - just after the first world war when I - I went with my father on my own. To - Hove. Wh
ich is near Brighton. And I would be what - about eighteen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You'd not seen the sea before then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No, not that I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You never went away for any kind of holiday as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Yes, country holiday fund which I told you the other - day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me about that again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well that was - well once every year of course, but - it was from school, and there was a - what they called first and second fortnight. See one crowd perhaps would go for the first fortnight
, 'cos we had only a month - school holiday in those days you see, summer holiday. Yes. We had a month summer - week Easter, Week Whktsun, fortnight Christmas. And that was our school holidays. And of course the first fortnight one - crowd would go and th
en the second fortnight the other lot - would go And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well, I went to - Downham on the Norfolk Broads - one year. Geest, in Norfolk another year. And of course the third year when I was - I was going to Norfolk then to Ware. And - the war broke out so it stopped it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That was the last one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes. Because I would have been - I was thirteen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It cost about four shillings didn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Something like that, yes, if I can remember rightly. Depend on your father's - earnings, what you paid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you know how children were chosen for those holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, you could put in for it, providing you could afford to pay for it, that's the only thing I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So the very poorest children presumably were quite out of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Yes. And of course you had to have a - sort of a - not exactly a medical but - your hair inspected to see if you were clean and all that sort of thing and if you weren't well you couldn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were there any other regulations like having to have a certain amount of clothing and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When you got there where did you stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh in different houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 In people's homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes. Like - anybody like who would be coming 
here like - I suppose - anybody that offered to have these children, as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I believe they still do that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I don't know, I couldn't say. Do they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When you got there would you go on your own or would you be with perhaps a sister?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
No - there was three in one place, two sisters and myself. I never went with any of my sisters. I can remember my brother going. But - I think there was either two or three in each - house you know. And they'd be school}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You could choose who you'd want to be with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I don't think you could, I think it was just placed - you know, amongst the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But you were all from the same school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Then was anything sort of organized for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, you
'd get some conveyance when you got there to the station, and - taken to wherever you were going, and you just sort of went out on your own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Once you were there it was up to you to amuse yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes, no - no - nobody there like - from the school to - in attendance or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So you were about eleven were you when you first went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, I must have been, eleven, twelve, thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 The very young children didn't go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 About ten I suppose as I went three years, would have been going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember being homesick at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you remember any of the things you did, play on the beach and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well really we never - never went anywhere where there was a beach. It was mostly countr
y. You see the - Country Holiday Fund they - Country Holiday Fund they called it, it was - all country. But of course the Norfolk Broads, when we went to Downham there was the - Broads there at the time. I can remember }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797  seeing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
people fishing and all that. But apart from that you just - went round in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 In the fields and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh mostly working. Working in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That took up the whole day did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well - I suppose up to - near enough - lunch time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And then in the afternoon, do you remember what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh out in the street I expect playing as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever go to Saturday picture shows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Never, we never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did some children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 He did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would you have liked to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well I don't suppose I ever gave it a thought - really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It wasn't something you wanted to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about any Saturday job earning money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, wasn't such a thing in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your brothers when they were home didn't have anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Sundays, when you were quite a young child you'd be going to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that in the morning or the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 As far as I can remember it was - afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And service in the morning at the church or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, there used to be a morning service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What denomination?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh it was chapel more than anything, Methodist chapel. Mm. Although I went to a church school. Mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were your parents both Methodists?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well as far as I remember they never had any particular religion. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you think they had at one time been brought up Methodist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh my mother was - had been brought
 up very strictly with - her father was - some sort of - preacher or something, I don't quite know really but - she had a - religious upbringing. But I think - mostly chapel as far as I - I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did she attend the chapel herself or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Not when - not that I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But she sent you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was the same true of your father, he didn't go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You think he'd also been brought up in chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm. No I don't think he - he had any religious - upbringing at all becaus
e - you see, he had no father and he was sent on a training ship as a boy. And - as far as I know was always at sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Yes. There's always - every year - Sunday school outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mostly High Beach or - Epping Forest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have to pay for that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I think we did. Yes. Not much. And you had - you had - we went by brake, what they called brakes in those days, that would be -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that like a wagonette?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, only - much larger you know. In place of - that's right, two seats with the driver and then two long seats inside wasn't there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr K. You climbed up to the driver, and then there'd be a - about six would sit - on that front seat and six could sit on the ba
ck seat, then you'd come down the steps and you could turn round up steps into the wagonette, and they'd all sit along on two long}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 seats. Used to hold about - twenty or thirty people. With a - pair of horses. Mm.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did any grown ups go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your mother used to go did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 So it was an outing for mothers as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, mothers as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 The fathers presumably were at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh they were at work, yes. Then you had your tea there didn't you. As far as I can -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you take your own food or was that provided?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
No - I can't remember about - I think it was - provided a tea - if I remember, a bun and - bread and butter and cake and a bun I think, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You didn't belong to the choir, did you belong to any sort of club or guild or organisation to do with chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. Oh Band of Hope. We went to - Band of Hope, we had to go there once a week didn't we.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That was where they used to sign the pledge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That's right, temperance.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you sign the pledge once or did you keep on singing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, you only signed it once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It wasn't a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. And then you went every week. And then you had an - once a - I don't know if it's once a year or
 twice a year, you had a tea, you know, like a little - sort of party in the chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What did the meetings consist of, Band of Hope meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mostly singing. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that something you joined when you were quite a young child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, that was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Seven or eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, younger than that, before ever I moved - to Custom House I belonged to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 About four or five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Five. Five. We went to school when we were there didn't we. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you have talks on the evils of drink and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Oh yes, there was all that - that was really for that sort of thing you know. And - yes, I was going to say - we were outside - I was outside - well tell you how young I was, I must have been about four, may - may not ha
ve been as old as that, and - we were waiting to go in, I had two brothers with me - and a drunken man came along and he asked me to kiss him for a penny and - which I did and I - I was waiting to go into Band of Hope. Oh dear, so of course they - a penny
 
was - oh a fortune in those days because you got - four - six ounces of sweets for a penny. And there was a - a sweet shop next door, of course my brothers made me go in and spend this penny and - share it with them. And then when I got home of course I t
old tales on me and I - I got into trouble for - for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You didn't get a punishment for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
No, but I suppose I got a good - telling off you know. Because there was all drunkards then wasn't there around about and - that's all they used to do drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 There were a lot of them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Mm. Those days, that's where - well that's the only enjoyment they had, I mean they didn't - that's where their money went wasn't it most of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your parents ever talk to you about drink and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, 'cos my father - did drink a lot. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Too much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 To my mind, yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You had to go and fetch his beer did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 He wasn't one to go and sit in the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, no, he drank it at home. He'd have it when
 he was out at work, but - he always had it - night time like - what they call their nightly beer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What would that be, a few pints?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 A pint wouldn't it be, or a jug. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was that just beer he'd drink or did he drink spirits and that sort of thing as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh he did drink spirits. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When you say you thought he drank too much do you mean more than was good for him or more than he could afford or both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well he could afford it or else he wouldn't have had it really but - I
 suppose - we'd have had more I suppose, we went - we could have had more really in - I suppose clothes and things but - of course we didn't go without and we didn't go without food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 That was the fate of some families wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But then your father was in a very good job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Yes. And we always had our - always had our - what we call best clothes you know and best shoes, which - some poor children never had any. Yes, always the Sunday clothes and then week}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 -}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 day clothes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 When those Sunday clothes started getting a little bit worn what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well then you'd take those - for day and then you'd have the new out fit for best again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 There were the two lots of clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What happened to the Sunday clothe
s when they weren't being worn? Did you have sort of cupboards you'd hang them or would they be put away in drawers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 They were hung up in the cupboard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But you'd never have worn them on another day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, not until you took - took them - second best sort of thing you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were there children round about you who didn't have special clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr K. They were put in the shop anyway.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But your parents didn't have to do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, my - my mother never ever - well I can never remember - her having to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your father, his job was quite a good job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Reasonably, yes, yes, reasonably good job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You were saying you weren't allowed to play in the street on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about working on Sunday, could you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No, you wasn't allowed to sew or do anything like that because it was Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was grace said at meals in your family and you said definitely yes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 It was an individual thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, just children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your mother hear the prayers or did you just say them yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well she may have heard them when we were younger but you just said them naturally - when you went to bed on your own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I don't know if there's anything else about the chapel that you can remember? Was it quite important in your social life at that s
tage up to the end of the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
What the - chapel? Well - it was your - regular - Sunday - you know, outing and - and at chapel they used to have - Sunday school, what they called Sunday school anniversary, that was once a year. Excuse me.
 And that was held - Sunday and Monday. And - those that could used to say - a recitation or - singing and I - knew a recitation that was - taught to me from my - mother from her mother, and it was partly - religious so mine used to have to be - said - up
 in the pulpit on the Sunday. For the anniversary, and it was always the same one. But ordinary ones or singing would be left to the Monday but mine being as it sort - more religious it was - Sunday I had to say my p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 ece.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Can you remember it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, about a dozen verses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You can remember the whole thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. Remember every word of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You couldn't say a verse or two could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes, I could say the lot. The Poor Widow.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would you mind saying it all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No. But it
'll read through here. My terrible voice. The Poor Widow. I knew a - a widow very poor, with four small children had, the eldest was but six years old, a gentle mother's lad. And very hard this widow toiled, to feed her children four, And honest pride thi
s
 widow held, though she was very poor. To labour she would leave her home, for children must be fed, and very glad was she when she could buy a shilling for the bread. Oh no - think I'm wrong. And this is all the children had, on any day to eat, They dran
k
 their water, ate their bread, but never tasted meat. One day when snow was falling fast, and piercing was the air, I thought that I would go and see how these poor children were. E'er Long I reached their cheerless home, 'twas searched by every breeze, w
h
en going in the eldest child I saw upon his knees. I paused and listened to the boy, who never raised his head, but still went on and said give us this day our daily bread. I waited 'til the child had done, still listening as he prayed, And when he arose 
I
 asked him why the Lord's Prayer he had said. Why, sir, said he, this morning, when my mother went away, She went because she said she had no bread for us today. She said we children now must starve, our father being dead, But then I told her not to cry, 
f
or I would get some bread. I quickly left that wretched room, and went with fleeting feet, And very soon came back again with food enough to eat. I thought God heard me, said the boy, I answered with a nod, I could not speak, but much I thought of that ch
ild's faith in God.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember if they clapped when you said it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not - no, not on Sunday. But of course they would for children - on the Monday but never Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Thinking about the contents of that poem, were you aware of children in London being often very much poorer than you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did your parents help any poorer families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't remember them giving your worn out clothes to anybody?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well no, there were so many children we passed them down from one another you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember any particular children that you knew whose parents had a very hard struggle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh several round about, yes, heaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 At the school was there quite a difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Not so much my school because - it was more of a - well, a sort of best school to the usual run of schools, I mean we only paid a penny - a penny a week, for each child, my - but there was just that difference because they were mostly all - shopkeeper's 
daughters, undertaker's daughters, that sort of thing you see. And if you couldn't afford to pay your penny a week you wasn't allowed many weeks and you'd have to - be transferred from that school to another school you see where - you went free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 The council school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you know why your parents sent you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
Well because we lived on top of it at first, when I first went to school. It was only the first - three - my two brothers and myself that went there. And then - of course we m
oved and the others went to the other schools, nearer, that's the reason. No in preference. Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr K. The school where the - younger sisters and - went to, or one anyway, was called the - Ragged School Union.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mrs K. Ragged School Union, that was the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr K. Agate Road School.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mrs K. I didn't know that was the school nickname though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr. K. Well, it's a nickname. IT WAS THE ragged school, what you call the ragged school that was. Mm. And it - but it'
s correct name was Agate - Agate Street school. Which was a very terrible street. Oh yes, shocking.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Abbeygate was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Agate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr K. Where families - lived in - three rooms downstairs and family lived in three rooms upstairs, and 
when I say families they were - six and eight - all crammed up ; 'cos I - I - I've ex - I haven't - lived in it but I used to go into these places as a boy.</subject2>
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mrs K. Well I didn't so I didn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You didn't? On the question of politics, did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, only to - create about L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 oyd George I can remember, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What were his views on L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 oyd George, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 He wasn't very good. By what he used to say about him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Was your father a Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, be La - rank Labour I should say. If they had a - views, I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You mean you think he attacked L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 oyd George from the left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 I should - I should say so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Have you any idea why he disapproved of L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7361842\charrsid527797 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 oyd George?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. But he was the one that brought in the - wasn't he the - the one that brought in the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Pensions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 The National Health scheme. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mr. K. But you see if you worked for your living you had to be Labour.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 MRS K. In those days, you couldn't have a view of your own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What about your mother, did she have any political views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not that I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you remember your father voting in a general election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 And your mother? Women had the voted after the war, 1919.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Yes. That was the after the war, when the suffragettes, 'cos we can remember those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But you don't know which way she voted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, I don't - don't think she ever did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 In some places at that time men felt
 they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from the powers that be, perhaps the employers or the landlord do you know if this ever affected your father, whether he was under pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not that I know, I never heard him discuss politics at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Do you know if he was ever a member of a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 You don't remember him taking part in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did you ever sort of paint slogans up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. No politics didn't enter our lives at all in those days. It may in your house but didn't in ours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 
What about in the street, do you remember at election times if the children were sort of sporting blue and yellow ribbons or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, the only ribbons I can remember was - Oxford and Cambridge days, those sort of things. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 On Oxford and Cambridge days did you support one of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Well, we all had our own colours you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 What did your mother and father do when they had a bit of leisure time, in the evenings, would they stay at home or would they go out?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, at home. I don't know, mostly read - well they both did, mostly reading, as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would she be mending a lot in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But she'd also read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did she have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Not any women's guilds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No. There's nothing - there wasn't anything of that - in those days, not round here anyway, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 No, just - might go now and again to visit her sister but - apart from that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 She never went out for a drink or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh yes, she - she would drink with my father but not on her own. Oh they'd go to perhaps now and again to a theatre or something li
ke that. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Would it be as often as once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh no, not so often as - well, yes, they may go on Saturday nights but - I don't think regularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Your father got home in evenings from work for teatime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 How often would he have to go out again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4339325 LK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 Oh not very often, depended how the work went I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7865103 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698785\charrsid527797 But more often than not was he home in the evenings?
