e a - used to have the lid of a boot box didn't we, and we'd - make all holes in it and - numbers on it and then we'd - sit and throw these - cherry stones in like see and according to the number then - they'd have to give you - say - say it went in numbe
r four they'd have to give you four cherry stones, you kept them in a bag didn't you.
